sentences: Paul Nathaniel Barman (born October 30, 1974), better known by his stage name MC Paul Barman, is an American rapper.
He resides in Manhattan, New York.
In 2012, LA Weekly placed him at number 14 on the "Top 20 Whitest Musicians of All Time" list.
Barman is from Ridgewood, New Jersey.
MC Paul Barman released his debut EP, It's Very Stimulating, on Wordsound in 2000; it was produced by Prince Paul.
His first studio album, Paullelujah!, was released on Coup d'Ã‰tat in 2002.
He released his second studio album, Thought Balloon Mushroom Cloud, on Househusband in 2009.
In 2018, he released (((Echo Chamber))), his first studio album since 2009's Thought Balloon Mushroom Cloud, on Mello Music Group.
